<h2 class="bold font-l">Terry Pratchett's Death</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Death from the Discworld series to revealed to be this. As best exemplified in his speech to Susan at the end of Hogfather. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TheAntiNihilist" class='trope-example-link'>The Anti-Nihilist</a></p>
